      "Insurance denied coverage for a completed procedure. The patient demands the office adjust the bill. The front desk feels attacked. The hidden risk is patient relationship damage. The leadership challenge is clarifying financial policies with empathy. The decision point is deflect responsibility or educate transparently. The growth opportunity is strengthening financial communication training.",
